<doc id="865310" wikidata="Q7031838" url="?curid=865310" title="Niescier Sakałoŭski">
<text>Nieścier Sakałoŭski (; ; 9 November 1902 – 13 November 1950), or Nestor Sokolovsky, was a Soviet composer.

==Career==
Sakałoŭski composed the music for the Byelorussian SSR&#x27;s regional anthem, which is used today in the national anthem of Belarus.

